texts: "Hey Google, set an alarm for 7.15am (seven-point-fifth-teen-A.M.) tomorrow morning."

"Hey Google, read Women and Power."
"Hey Google, turn the living room lights to blue"
"Hey Google, call my phone."
"Hey Google, set the thermostat to 20 (Twenty) degrees."

"Hey Google, sing a song."
"Hey Google, call the nearest coffee shop."
